teamcomps.title: Childe Vaporise:
teamcomps.description:
Childe is the on-field dps and applies a lot of hydro to allow Xiangling to Vape her burst. Xiangling is the off-field dps. Bennett batteries Xiangling, provides a massive attack buff and heals. Kazuha shreds enemy resistances via Viridescent Venerer artifact set and provides pyro and hydro dmg bonus to the team.

Rotation: Tartaglia skill →  Kazuha skill →  Bennett burst →  Kazuha burst →  Bennett skill →  Xiangling burst →  Xiangling skill →  Tartaglia burst →  Tartaglia skill →  Tartaglia na3ca spam until Xiangling burst ends →  recharge Bennett, Xiangling, and Kazuha bursts → then repeat 
Kazuha can be replaced with Sucrose,Zhongli,Traveler (Anemo),Sayu

 Retrieved from KQM mains

teamcomps.title: Hu Tao Double Geo:
teamcomps.description:
Hu Tao is the on-field dps of this team. Xingqiu is there to provide hydro application for Hu Tao to consistently vaporize her CA. He also provides good single target damage, damage reduction and minor healing. Albedo provides off-field geo damage and elemental mastery buff on his burst. Zhongli provides a strong shield which provides a 20% universal resistance shred and ensures 100% uptime on geo resonance.
Rotation: Xingqiu skill → Xingqiu burst → Zhongli skill (Hold) → Zhongli burst (Optional for the petrify, usually a damage loss)  → Albedo skill → Albedo burst → Hu Tao CA combo → then repeat
Albedo can be replaced with Traveler (Geo),Ningguang,Yun Jin,Fischl,Mona
